# get_irida_analysis_submissions
# get ALL analysis submissions regardless of type
#
# WARNING: this endpoint queries Galaxy directly for EVERY submission.
# With a large history this will hang for 15-60 MINUTES. Do not use on
# production VIGASP.
#
# The curl call is commented out. Output is served from cached test data.
# Cache: ~/.bashrc.d/test_output/analysisSubmissions.md
