}

# NOTE: IRIDA makes synchronous blocking calls to Galaxy for every analysis submission in the list.
# GET /api/analysisSubmissions has no type filter, no pagination limit, and no timeout.
# With a full assembly history this means thousands of sequential Galaxy API calls.
# DO NOT run this function against live IRIDA 23.01.3. Use the cached output, for demo puproses.
# This is an VIGASP hardware availability issue, not a bug in this function.
